    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- 正文内容 --><h1 id="第一篇blog-个人blog搭建指北"><a href="#第一篇blog-个人blog搭建指北" class="headerlink" title="第一篇blog&amp;&amp;个人blog搭建指北"></a>第一篇blog&amp;&amp;个人blog搭建指北</h1><p>[toc]</p><p>21点31分-2024.02.32</p><p>记录一下搭建blog的过程（hexo+github）</p><h2 id="下载node-js"><a href="#下载node-js" class="headerlink" title="下载node.js"></a>下载node.js</h2><blockquote><p>总结一下：首先，Nodejs 是<strong>基于 Chrome 的 V8 引擎开发的一个 C++ 程序</strong>，目的是提供一个 JS 的运行环境。 最早 Nodejs 主要是安装在服务器上，辅助大家用 JS 开发高性能服务器代码，但是后来 Nodejs 在前端也大放异彩，带来了 Web 前端开发的革命。</p></blockquote><p>请前往<a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/">Node.js官方网站</a>，然后下载。npm？</p><h2 id="输入命令"><a href="#输入命令" class="headerlink" title="输入命令"></a>输入命令</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">$ </span><span class="language-bash">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">$ </span><span class="language-bash">hexo init qarakuBolg</span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">$ </span><span class="language-bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> qarakuBolg/</span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">$ </span><span class="language-bash">npm install</span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">$ </span><span class="language-bash">hexo s -p</span><br>INFO  Validating config<br>INFO  Start processing<br>INFO  Hexo is running at http://localhost:4000/ . Press Ctrl+C to stop.<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>成功显示出blog网页了</p><p>安装错盘了，剪切回D盘</p><h2 id="发布到GitHub上"><a href="#发布到GitHub上" class="headerlink" title="发布到GitHub上"></a>发布到GitHub上</h2><p>更改<code>_config.yml</code>文件中的</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">title:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Hexo</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">description:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">keywords:</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">author:</span> <span class="hljs-string">Qaraku</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">language:</span> <span class="hljs-string">en</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">timezone:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-string">...</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">url:</span> <span class="hljs-string">https://Qaraku.github.io</span><br><span class="hljs-string">...</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">deploy:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class="hljs-string">git</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">repo:</span> <span class="hljs-string">https://github.com/Qaraku/Qaraku.github.io</span>  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">$ </span><span class="language-bash">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行结果：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">$ </span><span class="language-bash">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><br>added 9 packages, and audited 250 packages in 17s<br><br>28 packages are looking for funding<br>  run `npm fund` for details<br><br>found 0 vulnerabilities<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>先生成</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">$ hexo g<br><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Validating<span class="hljs-built_in"> config</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in"></span><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Start processing<br><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Files loaded <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> 231 ms<br><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Generated: archives/index.html<br><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Generated: archives/2024/index.html<br><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Generated: archives/2024/02/index.html<br><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Generated: index.html<br><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Generated: css/style.css<br><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Generated: fancybox/jquery.fancybox.min.css<br><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Generated: js/jquery-3.6.4.min.js<br><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Generated: fancybox/jquery.fancybox.min.js<br><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Generated: js/script.js<br><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Generated: 2024/02/23/hello-world/index.html<br><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Generated: css/images/banner.jpg<br><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  11 files generated <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> 537 ms<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再提交</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">$ hexo d<br><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Validating<span class="hljs-built_in"> config</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in"></span><span class="hljs-built_in">INFO</span>  Deploying: git<br>FATAL Something<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;s wrong. Maybe you can find the solution here: https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>需要配置github用户名和邮箱</p><p>这里我报错了是因为</p><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dts"><span class="hljs-symbol">deploy:</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  type:</span> git<br><span class="hljs-symbol">  repo:</span> https:<span class="hljs-comment">//github.com/Qaraku/Qaraku.github.io.git</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  branch:</span> main<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里输错参数了and出现了</p><blockquote><p><strong>User cancelled dialog</strong>: 提示”fatal: User cancelled dialog.”这表明在交互式认证过程中用户取消了操作，可能是由于没有自动填充用户名和密码，或者弹出了密码输入框而未得到响应。</p></blockquote><p>这个密码怎么重新输，我没有找到方法，但是我发现可以用ssh，只要</p><figure class="highlight dts"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs dts"><span class="hljs-symbol">deploy:</span><br><span class="hljs-symbol">  type:</span> git<br><span class="hljs-symbol">  repo:</span> git@github.com:Qaraku/Qaraku.github.io.git<br><span class="hljs-symbol">  branch:</span> master<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>还是这样？</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">deploy:<br>  type: git<br>  repo: git@github<span class="hljs-selector-class">.com</span>:Qaraku/Qaraku<span class="hljs-selector-class">.github</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.io</span><span class="hljs-selector-class">.git</span><br>  branch: <span class="hljs-selector-attr">[main]</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="安装主题"><a href="#安装主题" class="headerlink" title="安装主题"></a>安装主题</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/fluid-dev/hexo-theme-fluid">fluid-dev&#x2F;hexo-theme-fluid: :ocean: 一款 Material Design 风格的 Hexo 主题 </a>这里有介绍</p><p>我的使用</p><figure class="highlight gherkin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs gherkin">$ hexo g<br>INFO  Validating config<br>INFO  Start processing<br>WARN  [Fluid] 推荐你使用覆盖配置功能: https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs/guide/<span class="hljs-comment">#%E8%A6%86%E7%9B%96%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE</span><br>INFO<br>------------------------------------------------<br>|<span class="hljs-string">                                              </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">     ________  __            _        __      </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">    </span>|<span class="hljs-string">_   __  </span>|<span class="hljs-string">[  </span>|<span class="hljs-string">          (_)      </span>|<span class="hljs-string">  ]     </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">      </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string">_ \_</span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> __   _   __   .--.</span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string">      </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">      </span>|<span class="hljs-string">  _</span>|<span class="hljs-string">    </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string">[  </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> [  </span>|<span class="hljs-string">/ /&#x27;`\&#x27; </span>|<span class="hljs-string">      </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">     _</span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string">_     </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> \_/ </span>|<span class="hljs-string">, </span>|<span class="hljs-string"> </span>||<span class="hljs-string"> \__/  </span>|<span class="hljs-string">      </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">    </span>|<span class="hljs-string">_____</span>|<span class="hljs-string">   [___]&#x27;.__.&#x27;_/[___]&#x27;.__.;__]     </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">                                              </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">             感谢使用 Fluid 主题              </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">    文档: https://hexo.fluid-dev.com/docs/    </span>|<br>|<span class="hljs-string">                                              </span>|<br>------------------------------------------------<br><br>INFO  Files loaded in 1.14 s<br>INFO  Generated: local-search.xml<br>INFO  Generated: about/index.html<br>INFO  Generated: tags/index.html<br>INFO  Generated: links/index.html<br>INFO  Generated: 2024/02/23/hello-world/index.html<br>INFO  Generated: categories/index.html<br>INFO  Generated: archives/2024/index.html<br>INFO  Generated: archives/index.html<br>INFO  Generated: archives/2024/02/index.html<br>INFO  Generated: index.html<br>INFO  Generated: 404.html<br>INFO  Generated: img/fluid.png<br>INFO  Generated: xml/local-search.xml<br>INFO  Generated: img/loading.gif<br>INFO  Generated: img/police_beian.png<br>INFO  Generated: img/avatar.png<br>INFO  Generated: css/gitalk.css<br>INFO  Generated: js/boot.js<br>INFO  Generated: css/highlight-dark.css<br>INFO  Generated: css/main.css<br>INFO  Generated: css/highlight.css<br>INFO  Generated: js/color-schema.js<br>INFO  Generated: js/img-lazyload.js<br>INFO  Generated: js/events.js<br>INFO  Generated: js/leancloud.js<br>INFO  Generated: js/plugins.js<br>INFO  Generated: js/local-search.js<br>INFO  Generated: js/utils.js<br>INFO  Generated: img/default.png<br>INFO  29 files generated in 529 ms<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>对了看到每次更新blog都需要</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">hexo clean<br>hexo g<br>hexo s<br>hexo d<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="针对blog更换主题后没有及时更新的问题"><a href="#针对blog更换主题后没有及时更新的问题" class="headerlink" title="针对blog更换主题后没有及时更新的问题"></a>针对blog更换主题后没有及时更新的问题</h2><p>到GitHub上的action里手动更新一下</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
